        "description": "A4 Clear Waters: if HP was consumed via Suffusion while using the Hold Mode of Aquacrest Saber (Elemental Skill), the Torrent Surge at the skill's end deals bonus DMG equal to 45% of the total HP consumed this way, capped at 5,000 DMG. No eval-time conversion tracks HP consumed mid-skill, so this is approximated at the 5,000 DMG cap (reached once ~11,111 HP has been consumed via Suffusion, a realistic full Hold-Mode usage) as a flat add on skill_dmgInc. No bespoke bonus key isolates surgeDmg from dewdropDmg/thornDmg in hit_definitions_json, so this will also slightly over-buff those hits.",
